Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:08.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}忍住眼泪 我笑了笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:13.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}我们的去向会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:20.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}仰望没有星星的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:27.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}像许愿般深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:34.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}越是想越是无法镇定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:38.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}在那痛楚之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:47.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}唤醒未知的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:56.65,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}把爱传达给你
